definitions.definition: A rich , sweet dessert food , typically made of flour , sugar , and eggs and baked in an oven , and often covered in icing .
A small mass of baked dough , especially a thin loaf from unleavened dough.
A thin wafer -shaped mass of fried batter ; a griddlecake or pancake .
A block of any various dense materials.
Ellipsis of piece of cake : a trivially easy task or responsibility .
Used to describe the doctrine of having one's cake and eating it too .
A pair of buttocks , especially one that is exceptionally plump or full .
examples: Since I started doing squats, I've built up some serious cake .

definitions.definition: A multishot fireworks assembly comprising several tubes , each with a fireworks effect , lit by a single fuse .
